oofem.out
#
CDPM2 single tetrahedron - pure shear stress (only sigma_xy nonzero)
StaticStructural nsteps 200 solverType "calm" initialguess 0 rtolf 2.e-3 reqIterations 10 stiffMode 2 maxiter 10 stepLength 1.e-6 minsteplength 1.e-6 Psi 0. hpcmode 2 hpc 2 3 1 hpcw 1 1. nmodules 0
domain 3d
OutputManager tstep_all dofman_all element_all
#
ndofman 4 nelem 1 ncrosssect 1 nmat 1 nbc 4 nltf 1 nic 0 nset 4
node 1 coords 3 0. 0. 0.
node 2 coords 3 0.1 0. 0.
node 3 coords 3 0. 0.1 0.
node 4 coords 3 0. 0. 0.1
#
ltrspace 1 nodes 4 1 2 3 4
#
SimpleCS 1 material 1 set 1
#
con2dpm 1 d 0 E 30.e9 n 0.15 talpha 0. wf 148.13e-6 fc 30.e6 ft 3.e6 hp 0.01
#
BoundaryCondition  1 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 3 1 2 3 values 3 0. 0. 0. set 2
BoundaryCondition  2 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 2 2 3 values 2 0. 0. set 3
BoundaryCondition  3 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 1 3 values 1 0. set 4
NodalLoad 4 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 3 1 2 3 Components 3 1.e6 0. 0. set 4 reference
#
ConstantFunction 1 f(t) 1.
Set 1 elementranges {1}
Set 2 nodes 1 1
Set 3 nodes 1 2
Set 4 nodes 1 3

#%BEGIN_CHECK%
#ELEMENT number 1 gp 1 keyword 4 component 6
#ELEMENT number 1 gp 1 keyword 1 component 6
#%END_CHECK%
